name: Observe -> Internal wiring/connections in Power Supply Module,
description: Visually inspect the internal wiring, solder joints, and PCB traces in the Power Supply Module for signs of disconnection, damage, or interruption between the battery, internal circuit, and output terminals., outcome="No visible internal disconnections or physical damage were observed in the battery, LED, or resistors. A short circuit is present between PSU Output Cable (+) and PSU Output Cable (−), identified as 'psu_output_short'. No polarity inversion was detected.\nCurrent persistent circuit state [differences with the starting state]:\nNo circuit-level changes introduced by diagnostics.", precise_action_cost=70.0, cost_breakdown=[('invert_enclosure', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('observe_component', 10.0)], simplified_outcome=None)] 
